That probably could have been drawn by the same guy who

65
00:03:58,404 --> 00:04:00,125
programmed it, who was also the designer.

66
00:04:00,365 --> 00:04:03,448
But even that feature, I don't believe, was done by one guy.

67
00:04:03,468 --> 00:04:05,350
And what about that feature?

68
