00:09:21,699 --> 00:09:26,980
Part of the thing that I wanted to show you guys was on Hearthstone.

157
00:09:29,417 --> 00:09:35,762
the designers, and by designers I mean the two designers, were sitting in a particular

158
00:09:35,782 --> 00:09:38,985
spot and right between them was a series of posters that they had up called the design

159
00:09:39,025 --> 00:09:46,171
pillars that clearly stated the goals of the Hearthstone design effort. And I wanted to

160
00:09:46,211 --> 00:09:55,218
show you guys these. There's game for everyone, keep it deep, make it physical, great flavor,

161
00:09:56,059 --> 00:09:59,021
play fast, and win or lose the game should still be fun.

