00:44:06,880 --> 00:44:08,741
But it's something to think about if you're

719
00:44:08,761 --> 00:44:09,742
going to go in this direction.

720
00:44:11,283 --> 00:44:16,887
So finally, just remember that programmers and designers

721
00:44:16,927 --> 00:44:17,768
are very different people.

722
00:44:18,488 --> 00:44:20,190
They're not just different people.

723
00:44:21,408 --> 00:44:23,529
their brains are wired in a very different direction.

724
00:44:24,109 --> 00:44:25,410
And this isn't a bad thing, though.

725
00:44:25,670 --> 00:44:26,731
This is actually a good thing,

726
00:44:26,991 --> 00:44:29,152
because the best systems and the best games

727
00:44:29,573 --> 00:44:31,634
come from a melding of design and engineering.

728
00:44:31,954 --> 00:44:35,396
Design and engineering's way of thinking is very orthogonal.

729
00:44:35,416 --> 00:44:37,137
They're coming at the issues

730
00:44:37,177 --> 00:44:38,558
from very, very different directions.

731
00:44:38,918 --> 00:44:42,821
And this pushback is what causes the systems

732
00:44:42,861 --> 00:44:44,021
to be as good as they are.

733
00:44:45,622 --> 00:44:46,823
But because they're so different,

734
00:44:46,843 --> 00:44:48,504
you have to build that strong relationship.

735
00:44:49,052 --> 00:44:51,894
And like in any relationship, communication is the heart.

736
00:44:52,995 --> 00:44:54,276
And trust is the soul.

737
00:44:54,997 --> 00:44:57,058
You really have to come at it in this direction, and you

738
00:44:57,098 --> 00:45:01,942
have to realize that when you come to a programmer with a

739
00:45:01,982 --> 00:45:05,024
discovered task, you may be killing his abilities to

740
00:45:05,064 --> 00:45:06,085
succeed at this game.

741
00:45:06,686 --> 00:45:10,508
And that causes trust to be damaged, and it might futz

742
00:45:10,528 --> 00:45:11,389
with the entire team.

743
00:45:12,610 --> 00:45:15,192
Cross-disciplinary staff can be super valuable if you can

744
00:45:15,212 --> 00:45:15,993
get over the problems.

745
00:45:17,013 --> 00:45:18,314
And just remember, every day.

746
00:45:19,168 --> 00:45:21,910
that we're all on the same team and we all want to make something great.

747
00:45:22,230 --> 00:45:25,273
We want to be something, we want to make something that we can be proud of.

